line clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Имена:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/imya/valera&quot;&gt;Валера&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-fotosource field-type-link-field field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Источник фото:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://flickr.com/photos/cgines/4774343011/in/photostream/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;cgines Flickr&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
